# Intuition
Just find the first character whose count is 1 by iterating.

# Approach
Initialised an array of 26 length to store count of alphabets.
Then just iterated through the string to find 1st unique character.

# Complexity
- Time complexity: $$O(n)$$

- Space complexity: $$O(n)$$

