# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
`` As we need to return first unique character in the string.``
`` So we need to store character and its frequency.``


# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
`` So we need to use Unorderd Map to keep the character and their frequency in ``
``the same order as appeared in string. ``

# Upvote
